content:
This is a message in a second topic.

Topics are similar to email subjects, in that each conversation should get its own topic. Keep them short, though; one or two words will do it!
we should customise the registration page with a reference to HL7 community rules (GOM, at a minimum)
Is that something that zulip does or is that within our control?
I'd be happy to follow through with Tim Abbott either way.
we can configure that on the administrator page
